1d48			 
1d48			 
1d48			; 
1d48			; 
1d48			; define linked list: 
1d48			; 
1d48			; 1. compiled byte op code 
1d48			; 2. len of text word 
1d48			; 3. text word 
1d48			; 4. ptr to next dictionary word 
1d48			; 5. asm, calls etc for the word 
1d48			; 
1d48			;  if 1 == 0 then last word in dict  
1d48			;   
1d48			; set the start of dictionary scanning to be in ram and the last word point to the system dict 
